{"tid":1100022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「前特首辦」預算開支破千萬　梁振英曾稱每天回去上班","createTime":"2019-04-10T07:07:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T16:25:39.000Z","uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"d6d61415663efdeb8262c6e6730825c47d0aaddf","tid":1100022,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cy-18_JOpeV_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcy-18_JOpeV_1200x0.png&h=091ffbab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前特首梁振英卸任之後，前任行政長官辦公室開支大增。政府就財政預算案回覆立法會財務委員會的資料顯示，2017 / 18 年度前特首辦的開支達 911 萬，比上個年度開支增加四成。剛過去財政年度 2018 / 19 的修訂預算開支更加破千萬，錄得 1,081萬元。<br />\n<br />\n前任特首離開政府後享有多項待遇及福利，包括可使用位於中環堅尼地道的前任行政長官辦公室、有要員保護組護送及司機、還有終身享有的醫療牙科福利等。<br />\n<br />\n梁振英去年後接受《星島日報》專訪，稱自己每天到位於堅道的前任行政長官辦公室上班，工作時間跟以前一樣，目前主要有四項工作，包括推動大灣區發展、「一帶一路」、改革開放及全國政協副主席工作。<br />\n<br />\n民主派議員區諾軒向行政署提問時，要求行政署提供，三名卸任特首董建華、曾蔭權、梁振英相關開支。但行政署只是提供了前特首辦近年開支，顯示梁振英卸任後，前特首辦明顯增加。<br />\n<br />\n財政年度 開支<br />\n14/15 559 萬<br />\n15/16 583 萬<br />\n16/17 643 萬<br />\n17/18 911萬<br />\n18/19 1081萬（修訂預算）<br />\n<br />\n根據行政署提供，前任行政長官出席推廣或禮節性活動，同樣在梁振英卸任後大增，在  2016 / 17 年度只有 168 次，但 2017 / 18年度及 2018/19 年度，分別大增至 476 次及 1,177次。<br />\n<br />\n因「家庭原因」放棄爭取連任特首的梁振英，雖然身兼全國政協副主席，但他平日相當積極運用 facebook，經常批評民主派人士，近日狙擊《蘋果日報》廣告商，不斷發帖數《蘋果》實體版的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97-%E5%89%8D%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6-%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E7%A0%B4%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E5%9B%9E%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597-%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258F%25AD%2F&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTpUrr29XULmfQ5XcAAvzh4c%3D&h=a3c2713c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597-%25E5%2589%258D%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596%25E8%25BE%25A6-%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25AE%2597%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%2594%25AF%25E7%25A0%25B4%25E5%258D%2583%25E8%2590%25AC-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E6%258C%25AF%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%25AF%258F%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E5%259B%259E%25E5%258E%25BB%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%258F%25AD%2F&h=94eae2b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%B2%A1%E6%94%BF%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97-%E5%89%8D%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E8%BE%A6-%E9%A0%90%E7%AE%97%E9%96%8B%E6%94%AF%E7%A0%B4%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E6%A2%81%E6%8C%AF%E8%8B%B1%E6%9B%BE%E7%A8%B1%E6%AF%8F%E5%A4%A9%E5%9B%9E%E5%8E%BB%E4%B8%8A%E7%8F%AD/</a>"},{"pid":"c1d3f5b60fd3817a6771135d5c250c140ce6d805","tid":1100022,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:09:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e57db0f09e3aee36cd9e414d61dff522c391384f","tid":1100022,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:10:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"533a65082c8da26f8d0a2fcb29d939e5a89cc08a","tid":1100022,"uid":34804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:12:39.000Z","msg":"退而不休<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7580a57bba659bfb5979e0ad20391e07e53db631","tid":1100022,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T07:24:02.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>